ppak.cret.weather.types

Class WeatherType

  • java.lang.Object
    • ppak.cret.weather.types.WeatherType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Weather
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BrokenCloudsWeather, ClearSkyWeather, FewCloudsWeather, MistWeather, RainWeather, ScatteredCloudsWeather, ShowerRainWeather, SnowWeather, ThunderstormWeather

    public abstract class WeatherType
extends java.lang.Object
implements Weather
    Base class for all Weather types supported by Cret application. It stores all data about conditions, location and an icon for GUI. Implements Weather interface.
    See Also:
    Weather, WeatherArguments, WeatherFactory
